
                ----------Practice 1: Library Management System----------

1. Create LibraryDatabase class (10 marks)

    Class name: LibraryDatabase
    Class attribute: book_list (empty list)
    Class method: add_book() → Book object add করবে

2. Create Book class (10 marks)

Attributes:
    book_id
    title
    author
    is_available (default = True)

3. Initialize Book Object (10 marks)

    Constructor-এ attribute set করবে
    Object তৈরি হলে LibraryDatabase.add_book() call হবে

4. issue_book() method (10 marks)

    যদি book available থাকে → is_available = False
    না থাকলে error দেখাবে

5. return_book() method (10 marks)

    যদি book already returned থাকে → error
    না হলে is_available = True

6. view_book_info() method (15 marks)
Display:

    book_id, title, author, availability

7. Menu System (15 marks)

    View All Books
    Issue Book
    Return Book
    Exit

8. Error Handling (10 marks)

    Invalid book ID
    Already issued
    Already returned

9. Data Privacy (10 marks)
    Attributes private/protected করতে হবে

